{"tid":886149,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊大陸支付app既入一入黎","createTime":"2018-11-02T01:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T02:26:20.000Z","uid":22362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c296693f3342012d2736e37697cce03577b0d0a3","tid":886149,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:37:28.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】繼「轉數快」客戶早前遭人盜財後，《蘋果》發現本港兩大熱門電子錢包微信支付（WeChat Pay）及支付寶（Alipay）均出現漏洞，若騙徒使用太空卡（儲值電話卡）開設電子錢包戶口，有機會藉着綑綁他人信用卡，暗地從該信用卡提取現金為電子錢包增值，再把犯罪得益轉移偷走。據悉，近月內地暗網（Dark Web）大量出售不法的信用卡資料圖利，更「一條龍」教人如何利用電子錢包把受害人信用卡的錢偷走，受害卡主包括不少港人，專家促市民小心提防。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181102/20536389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536389&d=gTSXuPBTjA0KmX7YaBKoltWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=46a216cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536389&h=49f31039\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181102/20536389</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留意到有班打手想混淆視聽將大陸app漏洞講成係信用卡唔安全</span><br />\n<br />\n首先支付寶同WeChat可以用太空卡開戶口<br />\n但佢信用卡又可以唔驗證<br />\n所以先會有咁既漏洞<br />\n如果佢唔比用太空卡<br />\n咁班賊都唔夠膽用 因為好大機會搵得返佢出黎<br />\n如果佢綁信用卡要驗證<br />\n情況都唔會發生<br />\n咁佢都唔會偷到錢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以根本就係大陸垃圾app 既漏洞<br />\n唔洗再混淆啦</span></span><br />\n推到全香港知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce95cd0f33308fa2f4c6212025ef5b256b4815f0","tid":886149,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3926e5af387cbb215cfa7209d958929130e97793","tid":886149,"uid":175655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:40:20.000Z","msg":"一定要綁信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcef5e1da507a462bca2408aa55915373bc654aa","tid":886149,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:41:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>金管局根本唔應該俾支付寶同微信支付係香港上架</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4e921430274fcf5eed8d095e2db9ae25d5437f88","tid":886149,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:44:19.000Z","msg":"信用卡支付apple pay呢類先係最安全<br />\n你所有野用apple pay既話係<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span>比人偷到任何野<br />\n因為Apple pay原理係自己generate 一段code進行交易<br />\n段code用完一次就冇<br />\n就算你買野個時俾人偷左段code 段code都唔會用得返"},{"pid":"4f75f00d1d9f83db342dfe29d916a9c2935d9e4f","tid":886149,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"推比多d人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70439008a24cc658d5694b32e67d196ce504d86b","tid":886149,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:47:26.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲嘢擺吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714dce6d79368cb0254860feea56137a007f74ac","tid":886149,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70439008a24cc658d5694b32e67d196ce504d86b","tid":886149,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:47:26.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲嘢擺吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"sor 好少開post<img src=\"/ass